images.description: SDSS image of lenticular galaxy IC 736, part of Hickson Compact Group 59
SDSS image of region near lenticular galaxy IC 736, also showing the other members of Hickson Compact Group 59: spiral galaxies IC 737 and PGC 36871, and irregular galaxy PGC 36867

HST image of part of Hickson Compact Group 59 superimposed on an SDSS image to fill in missing areas, showing lenticular galaxy IC 736, spiral galaxies IC 737 and PGC 36871, and irregular galaxy PGC 36867
